{
 "name": "RPlog_SW1_Log_2000-08-05",
 "title": "A Brief Appearance",
 "summary": "In the mess hall of the NRSC Deliverance, the Quarren technician Kelvis Aquatica wearily fends off endless questions from the slow-learning tech Jinx, finally ordering him to just read the manual. Bazil McKenzie, now openly wearing his Intelligence patch and rarely seen in public, wanders in looking exhausted and orders a drink at the bar, exchanging only brief nods with Kelvis and the Archer pilot Lelila Jayespyer. Kelvis joins Lelila, greeting her with a kiss on the cheek. Before Bazil can settle in, his comlink summons him; he downs his glass in one draw and slips out again, his appearances as fleeting as ever now that he leads the double life of a spy.",
